{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "mf-go-collection-v1",
		"name": "MasterFabric Go API",
		"description": "Complete API collection for masterfabric-go — a multi-tenant, event-driven platform with IAM, tenant management, API management, gateway enforcement, and observability.\n\n## Quick Start\n1. Import this collection and the environment file\n2. Run **Register** then **Login** — the JWT token is auto-captured\n3. Run **Create Organization** — orgId is auto-captured\n4. Run **Create App** — appId is auto-captured\n5. Continue with API keys, endpoints, policies, and audit logs\n\n## Architecture\n- **Auth**: JWT Bearer tokens (24h expiry)\n- **Multi-Tenancy**: X-Organization-ID header or JWT claims\n- **Gateway**: X-App-ID header triggers pipeline enforcement\n- **Events**: Kafka topics per bounded context\n- **Observability**: Structured JSON logs, Prometheus /metrics",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [
			{
				"key": "token",
				"value": "{{jwt_token}}",
				"type": "string"
			}
		]
	},
	"event": [
		{
			"listen": "prerequest",
			"script": {
				"type": "text/javascript",
				"exec": [
					"// Global pre-request: set timestamp for audit tracing",
					"pm.globals.set('timestamp', new Date().toISOString());",
					"",
					"// Sync jwt_token from environment to collection if needed",
					"var envToken = pm.environment.get('jwt_token');",
					"var collToken = pm.collectionVariables.get('jwt_token');",
					"if (envToken && !collToken) {",
					"    pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', envToken);",
					"} else if (collToken && !envToken) {",
					"    pm.environment.set('jwt_token', collToken);",
					"}",
					"",
					"// Warn if protected endpoint lacks token",
					"var auth = pm.request.auth;",
					"if (auth && auth.type === 'bearer') {",
					"    var token = pm.collectionVariables.get('jwt_token') || pm.environment.get('jwt_token');",
					"    if (!token || token === '') {",
					"        console.warn('⚠️  JWT token missing! Run Login request first.');",
					"    }",
					"}"
				]
			}
		},
		{
			"listen": "test",
			"script": {
				"type": "text/javascript",
				"exec": [
					"// Global test: verify response time < 2s",
					"pm.test('Response time is acceptable', function () {",
					"    pm.expect(pm.response.responseTime).to.be.below(2000);",
					"});",
					"",
					"// Global test: response has X-Request-ID",
					"pm.test('Has X-Request-ID header', function () {",
					"    pm.response.to.have.header('X-Request-ID');",
					"});"
				]
			}
		}
	],
	"variable": [
		{ "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "jwt_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "user_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "user_email", "value": "admin@masterfabric.io", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "user_password", "value": "SecurePass123!", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "org_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "org_slug", "value": "masterfabriccorp", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "app_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "app_slug", "value": "myapp", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "api_key_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "api_key_secret", "value": "", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "endpoint_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "role_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
